data.name: label3.Text
data.value: When it comes to America’s favorite pizza toppings, pepperoni is tops. Pepperoni is a blend of pork, beef, and spices. Its flavor holds its own when paired with Robust Inspired Tomato Sauce and other meats.

data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Bacon and eggs, those American breakfast staples, go Italian in this quick pizza. You'll also find a creamy cheese sauce in place of a haphazard handful of cheese, and hash browns tucked in under the layer of meat and eggs.
